{"tid":869453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港殯儀館設靈　林鄭董建華梁振英花牌現靈堂","createTime":"2018-10-20T10:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T05:48:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc73160673ea99eade2e2a3cc1d9a71ad1e3b41","tid":869453,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾物理學獎得主、中文大學前校長高錕上月辭世，香港殯儀館今午設靈。特首林鄭月娥、前特首董建華及梁振英、國務院、中聯辦及港澳辦等均有送來花牌，其中林鄭月娥花牌放於祭台右側當眼處。<br />\n<br />\n白玫瑰、白蘭花及白菊為佈置靈堂主要花朵，橫匾裝飾所用花為白菊，其遺照為晚年所拍，遺照前為白蘭花及百合花。其妻花圈為白玫瑰，子女及女婿等花圈以白蘭花及菊花組成。<br />\n<br />\n多個國家部門、政府司局長及政府部門等均有送來花牌，當中林鄭月娥的花牌以黃百合及白菊等組成，牌上寫有「高錕教授千古光耀萬世」，另亦見多名政府官員，包括政務司長張建宗及律政司長鄭若驊等所送花牌。董建華及梁振英亦有送來花牌，暫未見前特首曾蔭權之花牌。另國家科技部、國家教育部及中科院花牌放於靈堂右側。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181007/s00001/1538900219922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181007%2Fs00001%2F1538900219922&d=%2FRxmjVM7Z6W960Lqc4hsBSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a543451b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181007%2Fs00001%2F1538900219922&h=14c39891\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181007/s00001/1538900219922</a>"},{"pid":"19c94cbd9de9d591fde65494141b2549b1044325","tid":869453,"uid":63154,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"以為係有人送俾佢地添"},{"pid":"fc7090550ccd75f74860068a152a2616a5afe444","tid":869453,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112d82580d732eb92af39832ebb245c7265b7971","tid":869453,"uid":23200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"仲以為陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}